A Twitter user, Callie Colstonhas grabbed the headlines with what she did when her marriage ended. The beautiful woman decided to burn her wedding dress and pop a bottle of wine. She said the marriage was abusive and brought her unhappiness. @calliesoncloud9 who disclosed that “she used to be married” in the tweet she shared, had a drink before setting her wedding gown on fire. She tweeted; ‘Sorry for the picture overload. I used to be married, but I’m better now’ Source